OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRain and low cloud will clear
OL,6,FOrkney in the early morning, then
OL,7,FShetland in the afternoon. Dry and
OL,8,Fbright for a few hours before showery
OL,9,Frain spreads north in the late
OL,10,Fafternoon. Occasionally fresh winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FBright or sunny spells and
OL,13,Fsome showery rain in the evening with
OL,14,Foccasionally fresh southeasterly
OL,15,Fwinds. Drier overnight for Orkney with
OL,16,Fsome further outbreaks of rain for
OL,17,FShetland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
