OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,6,Ffor Shetland for much of the day, some
OL,7,Fbrighter spells developing later. A
OL,8,Fcloudy morning with some rain for
OL,9,FOrkney, bright spells and showers
OL,10,Flater.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBright
OL,13,For sunny spells Tuesday and Wednesday
OL,14,Fwith showers at times, these
OL,15,Foccasionally heavy and thundery. Sunny
OL,16,Fspells and showers Thursday morning,
OL,17,Fcloud and rain spread east later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
